  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fine, so school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I started to tell you I had my confrontations because of-- it was more of my father's religious belief.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I loved and respected my father, so I did not want to do anything that could have caused any concern with him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I also was concerned about the belief of my older brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My older brother was even more religious than my father, and he spent an inordinately large amount of time in learning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes he corrected my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, he went through school without ever writing, and these things were important.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in these episodes there was a continuously increasing pressure that I should write.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This teacher made it a program of his, and I tried to conform with his requests.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For example, he asked me to answer some questions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did that in front of the class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some questions asked, four or five students before every hour.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for example, he tried to catch me in any inaccuracies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember distinctly, in one of them, he was wrong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told him that, sir, you must be right, but in our textbook in page 128, the 42nd line, it is written differently, and this is why I did not answer correctly.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the class was laughing, because they knew this, and, of course, regardless who they were, in this context, they were on my side almost unanimously.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at the end of fourth year, he called in my father and told him that the balance of power is shifting.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is true that the director of the school, [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Palfy ?], was protecting me, but now the district director became [INAUDIBLE], who was another fascist.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
